channel.title: 525 HYBRID PVP Door problem
channel.description: Hello, I am using a 525 source and its Hybrid PVP. I am wanting to move my servers home and I used doors.cfg to try to get into my new home. It will not work, so i want to just delete the doors. How can I delete the doors, I know the object code already, or if someone can be detailed on how exactly to do the doors.cfg :) oh actually its a gate that I want to open and shut, or be deleted. Thanks.

item.title: 525 HYBRID PVP Door problem
item.dc:creator: @partykid partykid
item.description:
@partykid wrote:

change the last number on both halves of the gate to 1, save, make sure server is not running, compile then run server
